
  <sn><md>### Soil and Environmental Quality


| Item              | Details                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Course Code**   | 07120201301                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| **Course Status** | Core                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| **Credit**        | 3.0                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| **Rationale**     | This course provides a comprehensive understanding of the interconnections between soil, water, and air quality.<br>It emphasizes impacts on sustainable land and forest management.<br>It equips students to address contemporary environmental challenges and promote sustainable practices in Bangladesh and beyond |

---

Course Learning Outcomes (CLOs)

Upon completion, students will be able to:

* **CLO 1:** Understand soil, water, and air quality<br>and assess environmental conditions effectively.
* **CLO 2:** Develop practical skills in measuring and monitoring quality indicators<br>and understand their implications for soil health and agriculture.
* **CLO 3:** Understand environmental laws and remediation strategies<br>to prepare for responsible decision-making in environmental management.

